  "subject": "Alternative MR replication method",
  "commit_message": "Alternative MR replication method\n\nThis introduces a new set of replication rules for topics:\nREPLICATION_EDGE_TO_FQDN\nREPLICATION_FQDN_TO_EDGE\nREPLICATION_EDGE_TO_FQDN_TO_GLOBAL\nREPLICATION_GLOBAL_TO_FQDN_TO_EDGE\n\nThis will allow some apps to design their own message replication path\nfor resiliency because it will use the FQDN of the central MR cluster\ninstead of using the CNAME.\n\nChange-Id: I09292733c5a9353ac494d2356ae995d59065a4e7\nSigned-off-by: dglFromAtt <dgl@research.att.com>\nIssue-ID: DMAAP-542\n",
